# Random Password Generator
project Link: https://random-password-generator-woad.vercel.app/
This project is a web-based random password generator. It allows users to create secure passwords for various online accounts.

## Features

- Generate random passwords of varying lengths.
- Include uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters in the password.
- Visual indication of password strength.

## Installation

To run this project locally, clone the repository and open the `index.html` file in your browser.

## Usage

1. Open the application in your browser.
2. Adjust the password length using the slider.
3. Select the types of characters you want to include in your password (uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, special characters).
4. Click the "Generate Password" button to create a new password.
5. Optionally, click the "Copy" button to copy the generated password to your clipboard.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

